Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.88,0:00:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Letters From lwo Jima{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}【硫 磺 岛 来 信】{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.17,0:00:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lWO JlMA{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}(硫磺岛，2005年){\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.97,0:02:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How did those soldiers ever manage to dig out these tunnels?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那些士兵是怎么挖出这些隧道？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Let's get a rotation in here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们换班吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hey, l found something!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}喂，我发现东西了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}小心点， 轻一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lWO JlMA 1944{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}(硫磺岛，1944年){\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.83,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hanako...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}花子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We soldiers dig.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们一直在挖{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.33,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We dig all day.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们整天都在挖{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is the hole that we will fight...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这将是我们以后打仗…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and die in.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}死在里面的坑洞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hanako...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}花子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.95,0:02:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}am I digging my own grave?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是不是在自掘坟墓？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Today, I head for the post where my men await.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}今天我前往士兵死守的硫磺岛{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.47,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I am determined to serve and give my life for my country.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我决心为祖国， 赴汤蹈火、在死不惜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I believe I have organized everything at home...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我把家里都安排妥善{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.51,0:03:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but I am sorry I wasn't able to attend to the kitchen floor before I left.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过很抱歉来不及拖厨房地板{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I had all the intention...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我本来要处理的{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but had to leave without having the time...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过必须赶着上路{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and I am still worried about it.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我仍然有点担心{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So make sure to have Taro take care of it promptly.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请你尽快叫太郎处理{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Damn this island! The Americans can have it.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这座臭小岛，给美国佬算了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Nothing grows here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这里什么都长不出来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt smells. lt's hot. There are too many damn bugs, and there's no water.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}又臭又热， 虫子又多，又没有水喝{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This island is part of Japan's sacred homeland.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这座小岛是日本的神圣领土{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There's nothing sacred about this island.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}哪有什么神圣的地方{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Saigo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西乡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We should just give the island to the Americans...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们应该供手让给美国佬{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and then we can go home.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}然后就可以回家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Saigo!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西乡！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What did you say, soldier?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你刚才说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l said if we beat the Americans, then we can go home.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们打败美国佬就能回家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You there, is that what he said?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他是这么说的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Yes, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是的，长官{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.84,0:06:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm Kuribayashi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是栗林{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Welcome, General. l am Admiral Ohsugi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}欢迎，中将，我是大杉准将{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How long have you been waiting here for me?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们在这里等了多久？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Three hours, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}三个钟头{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Sorry to hear that.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真是不好意思{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.71,0:06:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They wouldn't allow me to wire my arrival after what happened to Admiral Yamamoto.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}山本大将的飞机被美军击落后， 上级就不让我发电通知你们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l understand, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我了解，长官{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is my aide, Lieutenant Fujita.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是我的副官，藤田中尉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What's the matter, Admiral? You don't look very well.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}准将，你的脸色不太好{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's nothing, sir. The water doesn't agree with me here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没事，我只是喝不惯这里的水{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Sorry to hear that.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}很遗憾{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This way to your quarters.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请到您的营房{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Admiral, l want to make a round of the island first.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我想先巡视这座小岛{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shall l fetch a vehicle?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我替您调派专车{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No, let's walk.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不用，我们走一走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Walking is good for the health.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}走路有益健康{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt might be just what you need, Ohsugi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许你该多走路，大杉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So that's Suribachi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那就是折钵山{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You unpatriotic...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们这两个不爱国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}no-good peasants!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没用的农夫{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hey, stop it!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}住手{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.81,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Stand up!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}站起来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What are you doing?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你在做什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}These soldiers...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这两个小兵…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}were conspiring with unpatriotic words, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}说了不爱国的话{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l see.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}原来如此{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.60,0:07:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And, Captain, do you have such an excess of soldiers...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}军曹，你有足够的士兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}that you could put two of them out of commission?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}能把他们鞭打到不能打仗吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有，长官{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Then stop beating them.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那就不要再鞭打他们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Deny their lunch rations instead.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让他们中午饿肚子就行了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}A good captain uses his brain, not just his whip.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一名好军曹要用脑子，不是鞭子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是的，长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What is all this?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这些是什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}All this?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这些吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Trenches, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是战壕{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why are the men digging trenches here?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为什么在这里挖战壕？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is where the Americans are expected to land.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军会在这里登陆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Have them stop immediately.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}命令他们立刻住手{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But, General--{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是，中将…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And, Captain...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}军曹{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}make sure these men get proper breaks.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让这些士兵休息一下{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They look like they're from Mars.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们看起来像火星人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Stop digging!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}停止挖掘！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Stop digging!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}停止挖掘！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Just as well.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不吃饭也好{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}My stomach has been bothering me anyway.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我的肠胃不太舒服{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}A toast to General Kuribayashi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敬栗林中将{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}a fine commander.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一位优秀的指挥官{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Better than sake!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这比清酒好喝{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l heard he lived in America.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我听说他住过美国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe that's why he doesn't want us digging trenches.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许他根本不要我们挖战壕{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe he likes Americans.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许他喜欢美国佬{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No, stupid. He studied the Americans.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}才不咧，他是去了解美军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So now he knows how to beat them.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这样才知道该怎么打败他们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l heard from someone in the 204th...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我听204营的人说{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.25,0:09:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}that another general was supposed to command the island...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}上头本来是找另外一名将军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but he didn't want the job.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可是他不肯来这里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.09,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So Premier Tojo gave it to Kuribayashi instead.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}东条首相就把任务交给栗林{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Nozaki, you hear a lot of things...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}野崎，你听说不少事嘛{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but your ears are full of wax!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可是你的耳朵都塞满耳屎{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Anyway, you can't trust anyone from the 204th.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}而且204营的人都不可靠{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They're part of the Navy.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们是海军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l think this Kuribayashi must be a superb general.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我觉得栗林是很棒的将军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Look...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}瞧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.61,0:10:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}we're not digging those damn trenches in the sand anymore, are we?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}咱们不必挖臭战壕了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This heat is more than l had anticipated.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这里比我想像的更热{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不用多礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This island is bigger than l thought. l'm exhausted.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这座小岛也比我想像的更大， 我累死了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lto, reporting for duty.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}伊藤中尉报到{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Thank you for coming right away.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谢谢你立刻赶来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How much air force do we have available?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们有多少空军的支援？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}41Zekes and 13 bombers, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}四十一架战斗机、十三架轰炸机{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}ls that all?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}就这样？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.27,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}ln order to support Saipan, we lost 66 planes a few days ago.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们支援塞班岛，失去六十六架飞机{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will have to rely on support from the Combined Fleet then.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那就只好靠联合舰队的支援了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}ls this the current defense plan?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这就是目前的防御战略？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And what about the Army troops? Where will they be stationed?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}陆军部队驻守在哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't know exactly.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不确定{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They are under independent command of Colonel Adachi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们接受安达中佐的指挥{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You have not coordinated your plans with the Army?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们没和陆军协调作战计划？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}According to Navy rules, until the enemy lands--{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}根据海军军规，敌军登陆前…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is a real war! You are aware of that, aren't you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是真的战争，你们不知道吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This will not work.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这样行不通{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You are concentrating all your efforts on the beaches.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们把军力都集中在滩头{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- Move the artillery to higher ground. - But, sir, we just had them...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把炮队移到制高点， 我们才刚把他们…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}moved down to the beaches.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}移到滩头{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Well, move them back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那就把他们移回去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.19,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Coordinate with the Army and have them start immediately.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}和陆军联系，请他们立刻行动{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Fortifications at Suribachi are the priority.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}折钵山的防御工事是第一优先{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm going to walk some more.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我要再出去走走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- lt's pitch black out there, sir. - l know.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}长官，外面一片漆黑， 我知道{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This one is trouble.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这家伙是个麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Army commanders usually are, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}陆军指挥官都很麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Another letter?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}又要寄信喔？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You know that the mail only goes out when there's a boat available?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}船来了才能把信寄出去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l have a lot of family.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我有很多家人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Then how come all your letters are addressed to your wife?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为什么收信人都是你老婆？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Nosey!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}多管闲事{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Here, let me do you a favor.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让我帮你个忙{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.41,0:13:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Otherwise, your letters will never make it through.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不然你的信永远寄不出去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hey, what are you doing?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你在干什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l used to work at the censorship office in Tokyo before l was transferred.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我被调职前在东京稽查局工作{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You mean demoted.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你应该是被降职吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}''To Hanako: We soldiers dig. We dig all day.''{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}花子，我们一直挖，整天都在挖{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No, no, no. This will never pass.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不行，这一定过不了关{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Give me that back!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}还给我{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.84,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There. You'll thank me for this later, Saigo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}好了，你会感激我的，西乡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Next!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}下一个{\r}
