Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Are you blind?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你是瞎了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Can't you see the target?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}看不到标靶吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Even my six-year-old could shoot better than you do.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}连我六岁的儿子都射得比你准{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Do it again!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}再来一次{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.57,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You're an embarrassment! You call yourself an lmperial soldier?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真丢脸，你算是帝国士兵吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Tonight you will clean the boots of your entire troop.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你今晚要替部队的弟兄擦军靴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Go to the rear!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}给我到后面去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They should learn to clean their guns properly, rather than their boots.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们应该学会擦步枪，不是军靴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What are those tanks doing here?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这些坦克车怎么会在这里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Those are out of commission, sir. They are waiting for parts.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}它们坏了，正在等零件{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- For how long? - About a month, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}要等多久？ 大概一个月{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Taro, America is filled with cars.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}太郎，美国有好多车子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.92,0:16:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I have to be very careful when I cross the street...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我每次过马路都要很小心{\r}
