Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Taro, are you behaving yourself and listening to your mother?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你有没有乖乖听妈妈的话？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I miss you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}爸爸很想你{\r}
