Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hanako...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}花子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}we have a celebrity here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这里来了一个名人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Baron Nishi, the Olympic gold medalist in horse jumping.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}奥运马术项目金牌得主， 西竹一男爵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He will lead the 26th tank regiment...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他才刚从东京抵达{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and has just arrived from Tokyo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}要负责指挥26战车团{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}回去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.05,0:18:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Nishi is very handsome, and there are rumors of his womanizing skills.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}竹一很帅，听说他很会钓马子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.45,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But there are no women left on the island to woo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过岛上连一个女人都没有{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Lieutenant Colonel Nishi! You brought your horse.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西中佐，你把你的马带来了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}From Chichi Jima.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大老远从父岛带来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l used to be a cavalryman myself, you know.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我以前也是骑兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Of course, l know.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l've been looking forward to serving under you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我很期待能在您的麾下服役{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}One who understands horses the way l do.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}您和我一样了解马匹{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.24,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}When we used to ride horses through the battlefield...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们以前都是骑着马上战场{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}those were the good old days...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}能够骑马真好{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}not like these mechanized contraptions.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不像这些机械军车{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l could send for another horse...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我再调一匹马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and we could ride together.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们一起骑马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm afraid my riding days are over.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我已经不能骑马了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.26,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But tell me about this famous horse of yours that you won the Olympics with.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谈谈替你赢了奥运金牌的那匹马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}My stallion, Uranus.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我的爱马，天王星{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.64,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Oh, yes, this horse has a fine back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这真是一匹好马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l bought him in ltaly.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他是我在意大利买的{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They were happy to get rid of him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们很高兴能把他卖掉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.32,0:20:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He was such a wild horse.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他是一匹野马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.06,0:20:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No one could tame the beast, but l told them...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没人能驯服他，不过我说…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}such a headstrong horse...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这种野马{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}is a perfect match for me.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}最适合我{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Come dine with me tonight. l feel like having a drink.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}今晚一起吃饭，我想小酌几杯{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l think that can be arranged.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没问题{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How did you manage to get the Johnnie Walker?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你怎么弄得到约翰走路？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l drank some already.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我已经喝了一点{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm sorry. This is all we have.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不好意思，只有这点菜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's fine, as long as we have this.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没关系，有酒就行{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What is this empty plate?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}怎么会有空盘子？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.01,0:21:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l have told our cook that all officers will have the same rations and food as our men.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我跟厨子说军官和士兵吃的一样{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm sorry, but serving three dishes is regulation.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}抱歉，规定要上三道菜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Oh, but of course we have the right to be served more than three dishes per meal.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们当然有权吃不只三道菜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You're absolutely right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你说的没错{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.07,0:21:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}When you think about it...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}老实说{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.27,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}it is regrettable that most of the Combined Fleet was destroyed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}联合舰队几乎全毁真的很遗憾{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We still have some battleships left...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}虽然还剩下几艘军舰{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.08,0:22:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but we have very little striking power from the air or sea.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是海空的火力都荡然无存{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Nishi, what do you mean?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}竹一，你在说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.06,0:22:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So you have not heard about the Mariana battle?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}您没有听说马里尼亚诺战役？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.76,0:22:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Admiral Ozawa's carrier and boat planes were destroyed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大泽中将的航空母舰和战机全毁{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.34,0:22:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The lmperial headquarters...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}帝国总部{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}is deceiving not just the people, but us as well.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不但欺骗人民也欺骗我们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.68,0:22:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf you want my honest opinion, General...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}如果您想听我的意见{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.15,0:22:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}the best thing to do...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}最好的方法就是…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.92,0:22:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}would be to sink the island to the bottom of the sea.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把这座小岛炸沉到海底{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And yet, you still came?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是你还是来了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Well...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我猜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.46,0:22:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l figured your men were going to need all the tanks that l could bring.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们应该需要， 我带来的坦克车{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.77,0:23:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.42,0:23:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This must be it.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一定是这里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Yes, the enemy must land here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敌军一定会在这里登陆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.29,0:23:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Run!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快跑！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.86,0:23:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Like you were one of the Americans!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}假装你是美军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Go on! Which direction would you take?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快跑！你会往哪个方向跑？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快跑！不要偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.50,0:24:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hey...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}喂…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.83,0:24:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l think your general has gone mad.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你那个将军疯了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.90,0:24:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Look at the gun he has.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你看他的配枪{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He probably took it from a dead American.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一定是从死美军身上抢来的{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.35,0:24:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.86,0:25:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Break time is over.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}休息时间结束{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.93,0:25:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Back to work!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}回去干活{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.83,0:25:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Are you all right, Kashiwara?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}柏原，你没事吧？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.13,0:25:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You look pale.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你的脸色好苍白{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.54,0:25:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm fine. lt's just the damn water.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我没事，只是水不干净{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.34,0:25:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But...l...really...need to go.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过…我得去…上大号{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.56,0:25:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There will be a major change in our strategy.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}防御战略要大幅修改{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.47,0:25:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will dig caves in the Motoyama, Higashiyama, and Suribachi-yama areas.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们要在元山、东山， 折钵山挖掘洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.74,0:25:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will build these underground fortifications, and fight to the end.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}搭建地下碉堡、奋战到底{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.44,0:25:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- What about the beach defenses, sir? - Not needed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}如何布署滩头防御？ 不需要{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.08,0:25:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But, sir, the beach trenches are our first line of defense.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可是滩头战壕是第一线防御{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.98,0:26:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Without the beach trenches, how do you expect us to win?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有战壕该怎么打赢敌军？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.52,0:26:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hayashi, do you know how many cars America produces in a year?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}林少将， 你知道美国每年生产几辆汽车？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.69,0:26:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Five million.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}五百万辆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.33,0:26:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The Americans' technological advancements cannot be underestimated.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们不能低估美军的技术优势{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.56,0:26:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They will cross the beaches eventually.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们一定会攻占滩头{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.94,0:26:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf we waste our soldiers there, there is no hope for victory.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}牺牲太多士兵就无法获得胜利{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.64,0:26:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt is inevitable that men will die...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}士兵的伤亡无法避免{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.01,0:26:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but l never heard of an island operation without beach fortifications.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我没听过不运用滩头堡的防御战{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.41,0:26:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}General, it will be a futile waste of time to start digging tunnels now.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}现在开始挖掘隧道是浪费时间{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.21,0:26:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We should force the enemy near the island...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们应该趁敌军接近小岛{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.02,0:26:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and launch a pincer drive from the sea and air.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}从海空展开钳形攻势{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.35,0:26:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l agree. That makes the most sense.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我同意，这样最有效{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.92,0:26:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Ohsugi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大杉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.06,0:26:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}doesn't the Navy know?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}海军难道不知情吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.80,0:26:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The Combined Fleet has been completely destroyed off the Marianas.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}联合舰队在马里尼亚诺战役全毁{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.53,0:26:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The island is now isolated.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}硫磺岛已经完全孤立{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.17,0:26:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What's more, l received a new order from the lmperial headquarters this morning.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}今早我收到帝国总部的新命令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.24,0:27:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The remaining fighter planes are to be sent back to Tokyo to defend the mainland.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}仅存的战机要调回东京捍卫本土{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.62,0:27:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Outrageous! How are we to fight?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}荒唐！我们该怎么作战？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.42,0:27:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We do not have time for discussion. We should head back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没时间讨论了，赶快回去吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.33,0:27:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Dear Mother...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敬爱的母亲大人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.13,0:27:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I have been commissioned to a new troop today.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我今天被调派到新的部队{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.13,0:27:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}I cannot talk about this transfer now.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不能透露太多细节{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.14,0:28:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take good care of yourself.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请您务必保重身体{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.12,0:28:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Look at this picture.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}看看这张照片{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.69,0:28:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's some fancy castle.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}好豪华的城堡哦{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.70,0:28:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You know who this castle was built for?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你知道这是替谁盖的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Someone who was already dead.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一个死掉的人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.04,0:28:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They must have had a lot of money back then...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们一定很有钱{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.11,0:28:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}to build a castle like that for a dead person.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}才能替死人盖城堡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.84,0:28:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why are you reading that book anyway?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你干嘛看那本书？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.65,0:28:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We're never going to war over there.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们又不会去那里打仗{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.55,0:28:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We'll be lucky if we even get a hole in the ground when we're dead.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们死了能埋在地下就很好了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.35,0:28:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't talk about that. lt's bad luck.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别说这种不吉利的话{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.03,0:28:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}ls this the 312th?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请问是312营吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.16,0:29:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没错{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.43,0:29:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm Nozaki. This is Saigo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是野崎，他是西乡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.84,0:29:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.67,0:29:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shimizu, you can put your bedroll there.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}清水，把铺盖放在这里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.84,0:29:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There's an empty space in the back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}后面有一个空位{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.35,0:29:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't mind him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别管他{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:19.85,0:29:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}His friend Kashiwara just died.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他的朋友柏原才刚死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.19,0:29:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That used to be his spot.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那本来是他的铺位{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.63,0:29:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But we are all going to die.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过我们都会死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.37,0:29:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's the plan, isn't it?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不是这样吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.60,0:29:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}For our country, it is an honor.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为国捐躯是一种光荣{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.91,0:29:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kashiwara died of honorable dysentery.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}柏原是因为光荣的痢疾而死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.65,0:29:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shimizu, where are you from?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}清水，你是哪里人？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.65,0:29:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kanagawa-ken.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}神奈川县{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:56.62,0:29:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Ozawa is from there, aren't you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}小泽也是那里人，对吧？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.72,0:30:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没错{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.00,0:30:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where were you trained?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你在哪里受训？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.40,0:30:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe we were at the same school?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许我们念同一所军校{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.40,0:30:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不可能{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.17,0:30:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l trained in Tokyo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是在东京受训{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.77,0:30:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l trained in Tokyo, too. Where?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我也一样，东京哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.52,0:30:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The koho kimmu Yoin Yoseijo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}后方勤务人员训练中心{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.46,0:30:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hey...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}嘿…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.23,0:30:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}why do you think they put a kempeitai in our unit?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们为什么派宪兵来这里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.67,0:30:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't know.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.37,0:30:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He's not wearing the white armband. He's not kempeitai.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他没戴白色臂章，不是宪兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.35,0:30:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He went to the kempeitai military academy.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他念的是宪兵军校{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.62,0:31:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe he was kicked out.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许他被开除了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He acts like a kempeitai.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他看起来像是宪兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.03,0:31:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Look at his holster. That's not standard issue.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他的枪套跟我们的不同{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.67,0:31:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He's been put here to spy on us.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}肯定是来监视我们的{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.74,0:31:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why would he spy on us?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他干嘛监视我们？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.08,0:31:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe it's those letters you've been writing.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许是因为你写的那些信{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.05,0:31:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You should be careful.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你最好小心点{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.28,0:32:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Weed soup again?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}又是杂草汤？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.45,0:32:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kuribayashi is conserving our food supplies for the battle.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}栗林下令为战争保留食粮{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.85,0:32:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We'll be dead before the Americans even get here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军攻来之前我们都会饿死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.42,0:32:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And you would think that with all my war effort contributions...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我为战争贡献了那么多{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.79,0:32:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}we should be eating kasutera cakes or sandwiches.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}咱们应该吃蜂蜜蛋糕和三明治{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.80,0:32:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.73,0:32:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l ran a bakery in Ohmiya with my wife.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我和老婆在大宫开面包店{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.41,0:32:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Back when we could still get sugar...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}还有砂糖配给的时候{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.71,0:32:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}we sold ampan and kasutera cakes.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们卖红豆面包和蜂蜜蛋糕{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.22,0:32:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}However, his kempeitai brethren...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过他的宪兵弟兄们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.16,0:32:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}used to come and take whatever they wanted.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}经常跑来想拿什么就拿什么{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.93,0:32:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}For the war...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}说是为了战争{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.47,0:33:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}For the country...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为了国家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.74,0:33:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why bread?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为什么要拿面包？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.48,0:33:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We ran into those types at our clothing store as well.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们的服饰店也经常碰到这种事{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.12,0:33:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}When we started making sandwiches...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们做的三明治{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.92,0:33:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}they took those, too.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也被他们拿走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.19,0:33:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And when we ran out of meat and just had bread, they still came.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}后来没肉只做面包，照样被拿走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.97,0:33:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Eventually, they took all of our baking equipment for the metal...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}最后他们连烘焙器材都拿去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.98,0:33:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and we were out of business.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们只好关门大吉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.02,0:33:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l should have been a fisherman.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我应该去当渔夫{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:52.19,0:33:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt must have been hard on your wife...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你太太一定很辛苦{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.29,0:33:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}without the shop and without her husband.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}面包店没了，丈夫又不在{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.53,0:34:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Tell them to go away. We have nothing to sell.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请他们走，我们没东西卖了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.54,0:34:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Congratulations! Your husband is going to war.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}恭喜，你先生被征召入伍{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.03,0:35:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Thank you very much.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谢谢你们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.46,0:35:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm happy to serve the country.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我很高兴能为国家效力{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.40,0:35:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Prayers for your eternal success at arms.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我祈求你能凯旋归国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.47,0:35:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l beg of you! We have only each other.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}求求你，我们只能互相依赖{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.65,0:35:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is not the time.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你在抱怨什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.22,0:35:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We have all sent our husbands and sons to war.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们的丈夫儿子都被派去打仗{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.73,0:35:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We all have to do our part.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}每个人都要尽他的义务{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.77,0:35:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}At least you'll have a little one to carry on your name.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}至少你们家还能留下后代{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.05,0:35:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}花子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.88,0:36:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l can't eat with you like that.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你一直哭我都吃不下饭{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.42,0:36:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What am l going to do after you die?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你死了以后我该怎么办？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:15.10,0:36:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm not in the coffin yet.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我又还没有进棺材{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.14,0:36:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The men never come home, not even a soul.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}当兵的男人没有一个活着回来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.68,0:36:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They'll never let you come home.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们不会让你回家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.61,0:36:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't worry.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别担心{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.52,0:36:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And now, with the baby.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我现在又怀了小宝宝{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.84,0:37:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Can you hear me?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你听得见吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.88,0:37:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's Dad.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.15,0:37:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Listen.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}听好了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.19,0:37:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't tell anyone what l'm telling you now.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我说的话别告诉任何人{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.19,0:37:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's a secret.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是秘密{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.58,0:37:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Your dad...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你爸爸…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.65,0:37:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}is going to come home for you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一定会为了你回家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.94,0:38:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hurry up!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快点{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.58,0:38:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The enemy approaches!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敌军要攻来了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.82,0:38:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is ridiculous!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这太荒谬了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.79,0:38:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why waste time digging these tunnels?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}干嘛浪费时间挖隧道？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.76,0:39:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They are all going to die anyway.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}反正他们死定了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.43,0:39:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}At least he conceded to the pillboxes on the beach.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}至少他同意在滩头布署地堡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.95,0:39:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You wanted to see me, sir?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}长官，您要见我？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.82,0:39:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Care for a drink?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}喝一杯吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:27.82,0:39:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You have been looking quite pale these days.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你这几天脸色很苍白{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.63,0:39:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's the water. lt has never agreed with me.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我一直喝不惯这里的水{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:37.87,0:39:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's not good.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这样对身体不好{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.64,0:39:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why don't you go back to the mainland to recoup?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你何不回去本土好好休养？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.28,0:39:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l have commissioned Admiral lchimaru to take your place.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我征调市丸准将接替你的职务{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.15,0:39:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We are wasting time digging these tunnels.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}挖掘隧道是浪费时间{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.15,0:39:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}General, the island won't last five days without fleet support.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有联合舰队支援，撑不了五天{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.86,0:40:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We should fight to the death.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们应该誓死奋战{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.66,0:40:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The tunnel-digging may be futile.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}挖掘隧道也许没有用{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.80,0:40:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe the stand on lwo will be futile.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}捍卫硫磺岛也许也没有用{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.17,0:40:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Maybe the whole war is futile.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许这场战争根本就没有意义{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.54,0:40:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But will you give up then?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是你会放弃吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.54,0:40:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will defend this island until we are dead!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们要捍卫硫磺岛，奋战到底{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.84,0:40:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Until the very last soldier is dead!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}直到最后一名士兵战死为止{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.91,0:40:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf our children can live safely for one more day...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}只要能让日本的孩童多活一天{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.52,0:40:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}it would be worth the one more day that we defend this island!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们誓死奋战就是值得的{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.56,0:40:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Ohsugi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大杉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.36,0:40:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}if you have an ounce of pride left as an officer...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}如果你还有一丝身为军官的尊严{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.23,0:40:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l beg of you...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我请求你{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.20,0:40:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}go back to headquarters and ask them to send support.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}回到总部要求他们派出支援{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.06,0:41:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So the rumor is true? l couldn't believe it.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谣言果然是真的，我不敢相信{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.20,0:41:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm grateful to be leaving this island.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我能离开这里感到无限感激{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.77,0:41:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We may have had our differences...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们也许意见相左{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.94,0:41:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but l'm truly sorry to see you go.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是看到你要离开，我很难过{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.31,0:41:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}General Hayashi, it is up to you now.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}林少将，现在要靠你了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.08,0:41:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kuribayashi belongs behind a desk, not commanding war.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}栗林只会纸上谈兵，不会打仗{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.72,0:41:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l understand.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.42,0:41:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There are many of us who agree with you, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}有很多人的想法都和你一样{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.07,0:41:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Listen.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}听好了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.58,0:42:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The Americans are likely to land here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军很可能在这里登陆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:03.78,0:42:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Crossfire positions will be here...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}交战位置会在这里…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.35,0:42:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}here...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这里…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.49,0:42:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}和这里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.09,0:42:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The fact is...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}事实是…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:13.52,0:42:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}we are completely outnumbered in every sector.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们在每一方面都处于劣势{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.63,0:42:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But we have a great advantage.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是我们有一个很大的优势{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.63,0:42:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Can anyone tell me what that is?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}有人能告诉我吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.81,0:42:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The Americans are weak-willed and inferior to Japanese soldiers.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军比日军软弱和低劣{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.98,0:42:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Very good, Shimizu.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}很好，清水{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.35,0:42:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why is that?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.15,0:42:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They are not as disciplined...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们比较没有纪律{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.89,0:42:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and they let their emotions interfere with their duty.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}而且会让感情影响他们的职责{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.79,0:42:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That is correct.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没错{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.73,0:42:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Here is the uniform of an American medic.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是美军看护兵的制服{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.20,0:42:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He should be your target.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他是你们的主要目标{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.30,0:43:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}For Americans will risk the lives of many soldiers to save this one.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军为了保护他会牺牲很多士兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.30,0:43:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Understood?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}了解吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.92,0:43:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}General, may l speak with you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}中将，我能跟您说句话吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.26,0:43:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Please keep an eye on Major General Hayashi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请您留意林少将{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:23.93,0:43:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Thank you for your concern, Nishi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谢谢你的关心，竹一{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.50,0:43:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but we don't have any time to waste.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不过我们不能浪费时间{\r}
