Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:14.68,0:58:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Let's go. Commence firing!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}好了，开火！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:23.53,0:58:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Commence firing!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}开火！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:26.10,0:58:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Commence firing!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}开火！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:31.13,0:58:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.66,0:59:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The guns of the Kitakubo unit were destroyed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}北久保部队的机关枪被炸毁{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.86,0:59:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}All the pillbox units on the beach have been destroyed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}滩头堡的部队全数阵亡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:34.36,0:59:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}However, all other forces are intact...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是其它部队都没事{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:36.43,0:59:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and we estimate more than 1,000 enemy casualties.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们估计有一千名敌军伤亡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:39.20,0:59:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The pillbox destruction was unavoidable.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}滩头堡部队一定会阵亡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.00,0:59:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Overall, that is good news.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}整体来说，这仍是好消息{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.37,0:59:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How are the men holding up at Suribachi?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}折钵山的士兵如何？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:47.38,0:59:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Forces are intact.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}仍然坚守岗位{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:50.88,0:59:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:52.51,0:59:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What is the enemy situation?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大约有多少敌军？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:54.08,0:59:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Approximately 20,000 men and 80 tanks.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}两万名士兵和八十辆坦克车{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.49,1:00:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There has to be more than that. They still have men waiting in the boats.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}军舰上一定有更多士兵准备登陆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.92,1:00:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Currently the enemy front extends...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}目前敌军占领了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:04.89,1:00:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}between Suribachi and the south landing...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}折钵山和千鸟机场{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.13,1:00:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and Chidori airfield south.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}以南的范围{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.07,1:00:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Just as l thought... Suribachi and the Motoyama airfield.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}果然被我料中， 折钵山和元山机场{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:16.24,1:00:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They are making a two-pronged attack.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们从两面夹击{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.74,1:00:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们盯住他们了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:25.28,1:00:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}继续移动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.89,1:00:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's not enough! l need more ammo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不够，我需要更多弹药{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:02.28,1:01:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take his place!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}过来代替他！{\r}
