Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:11.36,1:01:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l can't rely on you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你太不可靠了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.76,1:01:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Go send a report to Colonel Adachi that we need another machine gun.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}跟安达中佐说我们需要机关枪{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:16.37,1:01:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hurry up!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快去！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.06,1:01:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Colonel Adachi is asking for reinforcements.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}安达中佐要求支援{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.70,1:01:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We can't afford to send reinforcements. Tell him to hold out.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有办法，叫他死守下去{\r}
