Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.12,1:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Do what you can to survive and join forces in the north caves.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}尽全力加入北洞穴的军力{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.76,1:02:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But, sir...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是，长官…{\r}
