Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:29.72,1:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This is our fate...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们的命运{\r}
