Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:30.13,1:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where are the rest of your men?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}其他的弟兄呢？{\r}
