Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:35.46,1:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's the same with us.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们的弟兄们也一样{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.34,1:09:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There should be an outlet somewhere near here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这附近应该有出路{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.81,1:09:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Be quiet!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}安静！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:55.55,1:09:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:36.69,1:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}So you thought you could blow us up, or burn us alive, did you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你以为你能把我们活活烧死？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:41.76,1:10:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不！求求你们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.21,1:10:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- Have we heard from Suribachi? - No, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}有来自折钵山的消息吗？ 没有{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:59.71,1:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Send a messenger!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}派传令兵去！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.26,1:11:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Lieutenant Oiso has ordered us to rendezvous at the east cave.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大矶中尉命令我们到北洞穴集合{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:21.40,1:11:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will make a run for Motoyama.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们要冲到元山{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:25.07,1:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There is no cover for two kilometers.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}两公里的距离没有掩护{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.44,1:11:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt will be every man for himself.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大家只能自求多福{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:37.75,1:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}See you on the other side.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}到了另一边再见{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:40.26,1:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf not on this earth, then in the next world.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}如果活不了，那就来生再见{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:59.01,1:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't run with the herd. That's where the enemy will fire.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不要跟着别人，会被敌军射死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.84,1:12:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Stay back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}退到后面{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.88,1:12:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's cowardice!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是懦弱的行为{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.18,1:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There is no use for a dead soldier.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一个死大兵没什么用吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:15.62,1:12:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}冲呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.65,1:12:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Wait until the flare is gone.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}等到照明弹熄灭{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.18,1:12:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我看不见他们， 不要停！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.94,1:13:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Crawl forward.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}匐匍前进{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:29.16,1:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What happened to the messenger?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}传令兵在哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.93,1:13:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He never came back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他没有回来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:36.34,1:13:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l will go to Adachi myself.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我自己去找安达{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:38.21,1:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Motoyama's transmitter still works, General.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}元山部队的无线电打得通{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.58,1:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why not try there, sir?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}何不试着联络他们？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.57,1:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Sir, these men retreated from Mt. Suribachi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这些士兵从折钵山撤退过来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:14.68,1:14:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What are your names?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们叫什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:16.34,1:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Saigo, from the 312th.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西乡，312营{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.51,1:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shimizu, reporting for duty.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}清水，报到{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:23.22,1:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You escaped from Suribachi?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们从折钵山逃出来？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:31.69,1:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How dare you!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}好大的狗胆！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:35.63,1:14:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt was your duty to stay in your position until death.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们的职责是坚守岗位{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:40.87,1:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You should have died...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}和同胞弟兄{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:43.37,1:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}with your fellow troop members.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一起壮烈牺牲{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.94,1:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You are both a disgrace.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们是日军的耻辱{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:54.92,1:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Get on your knees.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}跪下来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:59.05,1:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- But, sir-- - l said, get on your knees!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可是…， 我叫你们跪下来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:21.98,1:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't want you to kill my soldiers needlessly.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不准滥杀我的士兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:26.11,1:15:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Put down your sword.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把武士刀放下来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:28.18,1:15:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Put it down!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}放下来！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:35.92,1:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What's going on here?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是怎么回事？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.79,1:15:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}These men ran from Suribachi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们从折钵山逃出来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:46.50,1:15:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Lt. lto, l gave the order that all survivors retreat to the north caves.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}伊藤中尉， 我下令生还者撤退到北洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.68,1:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l am very sorry, General.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}对不起，将军{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:57.61,1:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's just...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:00.15,1:16:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Suribachi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}折钵山…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:03.99,1:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}has fallen.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}被攻占了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.71,1:16:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Now that Suribachi has been taken...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}折钵山被攻占后{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.54,1:16:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}the enemy will maneuver all forces onto the hillside.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敌军会调派全部军力到山腰{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:31.11,1:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We must move our command center north, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们必须把指挥部迁到北方{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:39.52,1:16:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lto...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}伊藤{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:42.79,1:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}fight for your fallen brethren...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为了你的阵亡弟兄…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:46.83,1:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}until the end.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}奋战到底{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.96,1:17:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Get up!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}起来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:16.70,1:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Major General Hayashi is leading an attack.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}林少将要指挥一波攻击行动{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:18.93,1:17:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We are to join him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们要去加入他们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:21.47,1:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:24.10,1:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kuribayashi's orders are to remain in the caves.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}栗林的命令是留在洞穴{\r}
