Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.19,1:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will take back Mt. Suribachi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们一定要抢回折钵山{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.19,1:17:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}遵命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:08.15,1:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where is Major General Hayashi?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}林少将在哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:12.75,1:18:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We don't know, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们不知道{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.75,1:18:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Who is in charge here?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这里由谁指挥？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:16.42,1:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm not sure.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不确定{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:21.49,1:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Stay here until l determine the plan of action.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}先留在这里，等我想出战略再说{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:35.61,1:18:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}万岁，冲呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:49.59,1:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We're dead.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们死定了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.06,1:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Pull back!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}撤退{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:59.73,1:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We'll get reinforcements.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们会找到支援{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.61,1:19:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}扶他起来，别停！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:16.41,1:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这东西卡住了， 真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:33.90,1:19:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why didn't your regiment join the attack?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们的部队为什么不加入突击？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:42.77,1:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't sit here like rats!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别像胆小鼠辈光是坐着{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.34,1:19:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Come out of your caves and fight!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大胆地出来奋勇抗敌{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:50.75,1:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where is your commander?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们的指挥官呢？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:52.48,1:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We haven't received the order to attack.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我没收到攻击指令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:58.02,1:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Didn't you receive the order from General Hayashi?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你没收到林少将的命令吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:02.19,1:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Kuribayashi countermanded Hayashi's order.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}栗林驳回林少将的命令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:05.83,1:20:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There is to be no attack.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}暂时不进行攻击{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:11.44,1:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We will take back Suribachi...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我才不管栗林怎么说{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:14.54,1:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}with or without Kuribayashi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一定要抢回折钵山{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:16.88,1:20:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}There are already troops on the attack. Get your men in order.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}攻击已经展开，命令士兵出发{\r}
