Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:23.11,1:20:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Your disrespect for senior officers...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你枉顾上级的命令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:26.32,1:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}puts your men at needless risk.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让士兵冒不必要的风险{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:31.16,1:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l suggest you go back to your cave...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我建议你回到岗位{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:33.32,1:20:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}or hand over your men.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}或是把这些士兵交给我{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:47.41,1:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Enough.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}够了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:49.04,1:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We'll do it ourselves.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们要自己去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:01.89,1:21:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's against regulations.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这样是违反军纪{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:03.59,1:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's the officer who tried to kill us. He doesn't care.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他想砍死我们，才不要跟他去咧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:39.36,1:21:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l won't go back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不会回去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:42.76,1:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l've had enough of cave fighting.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我受够了窝在洞穴里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:47.20,1:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You men are now under Lieutenant Colonel Nishi's command.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们现在受西中佐的指挥{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.15,1:22:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l will throw myself under an enemy tank.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我要展开自杀攻击{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:07.62,1:22:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l will take out one of their machines.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}抱着地雷炸毁敌军战车{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:22.37,1:22:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}爱现， 这里有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:27.97,1:22:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}好吧， 搞什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:38.78,1:22:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hurry.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}尽快{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:42.42,1:22:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What is the status?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}战况如何？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:45.62,1:22:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}A thousand men were lost...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}一千名士兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:47.53,1:22:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}in a night attack along Chidori airfield.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}在千鸟机场自杀{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.59,1:22:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why? l have given them strict orders not to kill themselves.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为什么？我下令不准自杀{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.53,1:22:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt seems that the order to retreat was not conveyed to all sectors.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}撤退命令没有传达到每支部队{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:57.17,1:22:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hayashi.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}林少将{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:58.94,1:23:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Damn you!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你真该死{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.34,1:23:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}And the American advancement?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军进攻到哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:03.44,1:23:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}A battalion is headed north and we are fighting back along the west ridge.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}有一营美军向北进攻， 我们沿着西岭一带反击{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:07.38,1:23:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Good. Once they cross the west ridge, they will be surrounded on three sides.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}很好， 美军越过西岭会遭到三面夹击{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:13.05,1:23:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}This just arrived.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}刚刚收到电报{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:14.52,1:23:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Read it.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}念出来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.63,1:23:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}From headquarters...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}总部急电{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.33,1:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}''We regret that we are unable to send reinforcements to lwo at this time.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}很遗憾目前无法支援硫磺岛{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:30.40,1:23:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We earnestly hope you will fight honorably...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们衷心冀望你们誓死奋战{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:34.67,1:23:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and die for your country.''{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为祖国壮烈牺牲{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:28.03,1:24:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.61,1:25:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}中佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:18.94,1:25:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Bring him in.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把他带进来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:35.86,1:25:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Bring him in.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把他带进来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.31,1:25:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shall l finish him off?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}您要我把他解决掉吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:50.21,1:25:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No. Treat him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不，替他医治{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.64,1:25:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}But, sir--{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:55.05,1:25:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Okubo, you would expect the same, wouldn't you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你也希望美军替你医治吧？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:57.85,1:25:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Endo, treat him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}远藤，替他医治{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.55,1:26:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We are low on morphine as it is.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们的吗啡存量不够{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:03.82,1:26:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Sir, the Americans would not treat a wounded Japanese soldier.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}美军绝对不会医治日本伤兵{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:06.82,1:26:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Son, have you ever met one?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}小子，你见过美军吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:11.33,1:26:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Treat him.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}替他医治{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:49.93,1:26:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where are you, American tanks?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}该死的美国战车，开哪去了？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.10,1:26:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Come and get me!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快给我过来！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.59,1:27:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}远藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:10.39,1:27:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How is the prisoner doing?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}战俘的情况如何？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:12.52,1:27:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He is awake, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他醒了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:17.80,1:27:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l will question the prisoner for information.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我要讯问战俘敌方军情{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:27.87,1:27:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大兵，你来自哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.48,1:27:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}海军陆战队，A连
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:34.65,1:27:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}陆战队员
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:36.15,1:27:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是问你的家乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.32,1:27:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我在加州住过一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:48.09,1:27:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你知道玛丽毕克馥， 或是道格拉斯范朋克吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.77,1:27:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大家都知道他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.24,1:28:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他们是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.27,1:28:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我在东京的住所招待过他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:08.15,1:28:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真的假的？你是名人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:14.79,1:28:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我参加过1932年洛杉矶奥运
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:23.09,1:28:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你是说真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:30.84,1:28:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这是我和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:33.34,1:28:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我的马的参赛照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:40.98,1:28:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真不是盖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:46.28,1:28:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}奥克拉荷马州
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:48.29,1:28:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我来自那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:51.79,1:28:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是西竹一
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:53.79,1:28:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我是山姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:07.51,1:29:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Damn.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}可恶{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:11.11,1:29:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l've had enough of this.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我受够了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.34,1:29:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm going to surrender.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我要投降{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:19.62,1:29:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Go ahead and arrest me.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}尽管逮捕我吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:22.79,1:29:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't care anymore. That's what you were put here for, isn't it?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我不管了， 你不是来监视我们的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:27.96,1:29:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}To report treasonous thoughts.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}检举我们叛国的思想{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:34.93,1:29:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l was put here because...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我来这里的原因是…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.20,1:29:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l was discharged from the kempeitai.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我被宪兵队开除{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:43.57,1:29:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Discharged?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}开除？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:49.38,1:29:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l had only been in service for five days.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我只服役了五天{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.92,1:29:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shimizu...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}清水{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:57.15,1:29:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}you must always be firm.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你一定要心狠手辣{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:01.06,1:30:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Any mercy and people will take advantage of you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不然就会被老百姓骑到头上{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:10.77,1:30:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That's unpatriotic.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这户人家不爱国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:12.24,1:30:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Go sort it out, Shimizu.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把他们揪出来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.45,1:30:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You do not have the lmperial flag properly displayed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为何你们没有悬挂帝国国旗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:29.45,1:30:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm sorry.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}对不起{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:30.86,1:30:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}My husband has gone to war and l couldn't put it up myself.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我先生入伍，我自己挂不上去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.56,1:30:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt is unpatriotic not to have the flag displayed.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不悬挂国旗就是不爱国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.43,1:30:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf you help me, l'll put it up now.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}请你帮我把它挂上去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.22,1:31:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Get that dog to shut up.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让那只臭狗闭嘴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:03.72,1:31:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What was that, sir?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}您说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:06.06,1:31:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}That dog is a nuisance. lt is disruptive of Army communications.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那只狗会干扰军队的通讯{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:10.90,1:31:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l am very sorry, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真是对不起{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:13.96,1:31:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:16.27,1:31:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}安静！安静！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:19.34,1:31:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Shimizu. Dispose of the dog.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}清水，把小狗解决掉{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:22.74,1:31:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We can't have a dog interfering with important military commands.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不能让一只小狗干扰重要军令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:32.08,1:31:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take the dog in the back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把小狗带到后面{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:34.05,1:31:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's only a dog.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他只是一只狗{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:35.65,1:31:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt won't happen again.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}以后不会乱吠了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.69,1:31:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take it out back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把他带到后面{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:40.59,1:31:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Keep the children inside.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}带小孩子进去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:43.43,1:31:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hurry up.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快点{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.01,1:32:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take the dog into the house and keep him quiet...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把狗带进屋里，别让他乱吠{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:36.05,1:32:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and never let him out.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}千万别让他跑出去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:37.28,1:32:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真是多谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:49.23,1:32:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's taken care of, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}长官，已经解决了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:29.13,1:33:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Are you trying to make a fool out of me?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你把我当傻瓜吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:32.90,1:33:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf you can't even shoot a dog, you'll never be able to handle the Reds.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你连一只小狗不敢射杀， 就对付不了共产党{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:39.98,1:33:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You are unpatriotic!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你根本就不爱国{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:47.62,1:33:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l was discharged for insubordination...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我因为不服从命令被开除{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:51.19,1:33:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and sent here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}然后被调派到这里{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:55.99,1:33:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.70,1:34:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't look so glum, Shimizu.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别哭丧着一副脸{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.00,1:34:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}At least now only the enemy hates you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}至少现在只有敌军恨你{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:12.74,1:34:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't blame the dog.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我并不怪那只小狗{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:40.27,1:34:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Taro...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}太郎{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:41.87,1:34:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}tonight I attended my farewell party.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}今晚我出席我的惜别晚宴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:45.41,1:34:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}The wives also attended, so there was a lot of fuss.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}军官夫人也来了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:48.11,1:34:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Greeting all the ladies...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我得一一向她们致意{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:51.28,1:34:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}kept me from enjoying the food.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}害我无法好好享用大餐{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:56.79,1:34:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}各位先生女士，请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:01.29,1:35:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}今晚的贵宾来自日本帝国
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:05.43,1:35:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}栗林上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:08.10,1:35:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这份礼物代表我们的友谊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:11.14,1:35:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}1911年份寇特点四五手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.64,1:35:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}每名骑兵都应该使用的配枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:21.98,1:35:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谢谢你这份美好的礼物和友谊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.98,1:35:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我会想念你的， 不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:33.46,1:35:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}各位，请就座，享用晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:40.73,1:35:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:44.17,1:35:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:50.24,1:35:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让我来问栗林上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:52.74,1:35:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你不介意我叫你粟上校吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:56.45,1:35:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}上校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.45,1:36:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你对美日战争有什么看法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:04.69,1:36:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我相信他们会是很好的盟军
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:08.59,1:36:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}她是说美国和日本打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:12.36,1:36:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}日本最不应该和美国打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:16.80,1:36:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是万一不幸发生战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:19.27,1:36:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我将为祖国尽忠职守
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:23.27,1:36:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我老公和你作战，你会射杀他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:27.81,1:36:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我会遵守我的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:30.88,1:36:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:33.45,1:36:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}或是国家的信念？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:36.89,1:36:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}难道有所不同吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:39.79,1:36:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你果然是真正的军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:43.06,1:36:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}那就太糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:44.86,1:36:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}老公，这代表你死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:47.46,1:36:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不，绝对不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:08.49,1:37:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}山姆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:39.52,1:37:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}ls there any information of the enemy's plan?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这上面有敌军的战略吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:42.35,1:37:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}No, it's just a letter.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有，这只是一封信{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:46.42,1:37:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's from his mother.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}来自他的母亲{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:50.69,1:37:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}''Sam...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}山姆{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:52.80,1:37:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l have mailed you a couple of books to read.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我寄了几本书给你看{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:55.77,1:37:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l hope that you like them.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}希望你会喜欢{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:58.70,1:37:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Yesterday...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}昨天…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:00.44,1:38:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}the dogs dug a hole under the fence.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}家里的狗在篱笆下挖了洞{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:06.58,1:38:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They ran all over the neighborhood.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}钻到邻居家的院子乱跑{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:11.92,1:38:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}By the time we found them...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}等我们找到他们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:15.32,1:38:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}the Harrisons' roosters were terrorized.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}哈里逊家的公鸡被吓坏了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:21.12,1:38:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Don't worry about us.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}别替我们担心{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:25.23,1:38:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Just take care of yourself and come back safely.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你要好好保重，安全回家{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:29.67,1:38:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Remember what l said to you...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}记住我跟你说过的话{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:37.01,1:38:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}always do what is right...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}永远要做正确的事{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:39.74,1:38:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}because it is right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}因为这样做才对{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:43.11,1:38:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l pray for a speedy end to the war...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我祈祷战争尽快结束{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:46.95,1:38:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and your safe return.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你能早日安全归来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:49.95,1:38:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Love, Mom.''{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}爱你的母亲{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:01.40,1:39:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}敌袭！炸弹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:04.87,1:39:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快点！快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.70,1:39:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:18.95,1:39:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}中佐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:21.49,1:39:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}远藤！远藤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:25.96,1:39:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm sorry, sir. There is no more medicine.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}中佐！， 对不起，药物用完了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:28.73,1:39:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt's all right. l'm useless now. Go help the others!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}算了，我没用了，去救别人吧{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:32.86,1:39:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:03.25,1:41:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Okubo, come here.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大久保，过来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:12.00,1:41:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}How are we on ammunition?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}弹药还剩多少？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:15.83,1:41:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Not good, sir.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}不多{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:19.80,1:41:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Our mortars have been taken out...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}迫击炮全毁{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:22.57,1:41:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and we're out of machine gun ammo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}机关枪的弹药也耗尽{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:26.24,1:41:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We have only our rifles.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们只剩下步枪{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:31.65,1:41:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Okubo...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大久保{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:32.82,1:41:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}you are now in charge of the men.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你负责指挥连队{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:41.36,1:41:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We can no longer hold this area.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这地方已经守不住了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:43.69,1:41:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You must guide the rest of the men north.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你要带领他们向北前进{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:49.87,1:41:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Take whatever food and ammo we have left.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把剩下的粮食和弹药带走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:54.44,1:41:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What about you, sir?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}长官，那您呢？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:00.21,1:42:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm tired of sharing this cave with all of you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我受够了和你们挤在这个洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:04.48,1:42:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm a one-man show from here on out.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我要一个人好好享用一下{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:07.35,1:42:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What are you talking about, sir?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}您在说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:10.49,1:42:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Your first order of business...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你的第一个指令{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:14.83,1:42:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}is to find some water.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是要找到水{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:43.55,1:42:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Men...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}弟兄们{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:46.19,1:42:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}do your best.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}尽全力奋战{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:49.33,1:42:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Do what is right...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}永远要做正确的事{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:55.57,1:42:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}because it is right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}因为这样做才对{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:00.00,1:43:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Understood?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}明白吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.84,1:43:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}是， 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:09.05,1:43:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l will make sure that they send you medicine and food.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我会请他们送药物和粮食给你{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:16.25,1:43:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lt has been a great honor...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西联队长， 能够在您的麾下服役{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:19.02,1:43:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}to serve...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}让我感到…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:21.56,1:43:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}under you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}无比的光荣{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:40.74,1:43:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:55.19,1:43:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}大久保
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:02.17,1:44:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Hand me my rifle.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}把我的步枪给我{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:27.52,1:44:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'm sorry, Okubo.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}对不起，大久保{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:49.54,1:45:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Why am l not getting any reports? Have we heard from Admiral lchimaru?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}怎么都没报告？市丸准将没消息？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:52.91,1:45:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- No, sir. - What about Nishi or Hayashi?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有，长官， 西中佐或林少将呢？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:58.11,1:46:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- Send out messengers! - We have. Many times.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}派出传令兵， 我们派了很多个{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:01.42,1:46:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}None of them have come back.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}没有一个回来{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:03.65,1:46:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You can't plan strategy like this!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}这样不能策划战略{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:13.06,1:46:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}西乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:16.60,1:46:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l have been thinking about what Lt. Colonel Nishi said.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我在想西中佐说的话{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:20.87,1:46:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He's right.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他说的对{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:27.54,1:46:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l don't know anything about the enemy.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我对敌军一无所知{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:31.21,1:46:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l believed that the Americans were cowards...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我以为美军都是懦夫{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:41.02,1:46:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but they weren't.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是他们并不是{\r}
