Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:55.37,1:46:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but that American soldier...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是那个美国大兵…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:04.85,1:47:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}his mother's words...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他母亲说的话…{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:10.92,1:47:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}were the same as my mother's.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}跟我母亲说的话一样{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:14.26,1:47:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l want to fulfill my duty for the general...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我想要为将军尽忠职守{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:19.16,1:47:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}and our country...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}为祖国壮烈牺牲{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:23.07,1:47:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}but l don't want to die for nothing.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}但是我不想毫无意义地死去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:31.21,1:47:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}What do you think?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你觉得呢？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:44.79,1:47:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你...{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:47.19,1:47:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}haven't lived enough to realize...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}还没有足够的历练， 让你了解到{\r}
