Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:05.61,1:48:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Will you surrender with me?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你肯和我一起投降吗？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:29.23,1:48:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Careful.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}小心点{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:34.17,1:48:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}They'll notice if we leave together. You go first.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我们一起走会被看到， 你先走{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.94,1:48:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l'll make up an excuse.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我替你找一个藉口{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:40.88,1:48:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}After a while, l'll tell them l'm going to check on you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}然后我会说我要去找你{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:43.68,1:48:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}We'll be gone before they even notice.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}趁他们不注意偷溜{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:49.09,1:48:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Pretend that you have dysentery.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}假装你有痢疾{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:51.96,1:48:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Give me your dysentery look.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}装出你快忍不住的样子{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:04.13,1:49:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l guess that'll have to do.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我猜这样就行了{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:14.78,1:49:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where are you going?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你要去哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:16.68,1:49:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}l've got dysentery.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我有痢疾{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:18.78,1:49:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You're going to surrender, aren't you?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你要去投降，对吧？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:20.88,1:49:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}lf you are, take me with you.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}带我一起去{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:23.62,1:49:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}- l've had enough of this war. - Be quiet!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}我受够了这场战争， 安静！{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:34.70,1:49:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Where are you going?{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们要去哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:37.43,1:49:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}He said he wasn't feeling well. lt could be dysentery.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}他不太舒服，可能是痢疾{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:40.07,1:49:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}You two! Stop!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你们给我站住{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:47.11,1:49:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Sir, maybe they got spooked.{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}也许他们只是被吓到{\r}
