Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:55.20,1:51:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Did you hear...{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}你有没有听说？{\r}
