Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:40.78,1:53:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnTahoma\fs10\b0}Lieutenant!{\r}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs17\b0}中尉！{\r}
